OL,3,CPolice behaved 'appropriately' before
OL,4,Cboy's fatal e-bike crash
OL,6,FPolice officers behaved
OL,7,F"appropriately" when they briefly
OL,8,Ffollowed a 15-year-old boy on an e-
OL,9,Fbike before he fatally collided with
OL,10,Fan ambulance, a report has found.
OL,12,FAn inquest into the death of Saul
OL,13,FCookson heard he was riding a Sur-Ron
OL,14,Fe-bike in Salford, Greater Manchester,
OL,15,Fwhen the incident took place at about
OL,16,F2pm on 8 June 2023.
