OL,3,CPolice behaved 'appropriately' before
OL,4,Cboy's fatal e-bike crash
OL,6,FParamedics treated him at the scene,
OL,7,Fbut he suffered multiple traumatic
OL,8,Finjuries from the collision in
OL,9,FLangworthy Road and died in hospital
OL,10,Fshortly afterwards.
OL,12,FAn inquest jury at Bolton Coroner's
OL,13,FCourt has concluded that the two
OL,14,Fofficers in a patrol car had not
OL,15,Fengaged in a pursuit of the youngster.
OL,17,FThe court heard that the officers
OL,18,Ffollowed Saul for a short period until
OL,19,Fhe slipped past a set of bollards and
OL,20,Fwent on to hit the moving ambulance.
