OL,3,CPolice behaved 'appropriately' before
OL,4,Cboy's fatal e-bike crash
OL,6,FThe police watchdog said the evidence
OL,7,Findicated that the extent of the
OL,8,Fpolice contact with Saul was brief and
OL,9,Flasted approximately 25 seconds from
OL,10,Fwhen officers first saw the e-bike to
OL,11,Fwhen it collided with the ambulance.
OL,13,FThe first opportunity the ambulance
OL,14,Fdriver would have had to see Saul was
OL,15,F0.6 seconds prior to the collision,
OL,16,Fadded the IOPC.
