OL,3,CPolice behaved 'appropriately' before
OL,4,Cboy's fatal e-bike crash
OL,6,FIOPC regional director Catherine Bates
OL,7,Fsaid: "Any death on our roads is a
OL,8,Ftragedy and sadly in this instance a
OL,9,Fboy has lost his life and our thoughts
OL,10,Fremain with his family, friends and
OL,11,Fall those affected.
OL,13,F"Our investigation was independent of
OL,14,Fthe police and aimed to understand
OL,15,Fevents leading up to the collision. We
OL,16,Ffound the officers acted appropriately
OL,17,Fand in line with procedures.
