OL,6,F"The evidence we gathered was provided
OL,7,Fto the coroner to assist with the
OL,8,Finquest proceedings, which we hope has
OL,9,Fhelped answer some of the families'
OL,10,Fquestions about that day."
OL,12,FFollowing his death, Saul's mother
OL,13,FEmma Frendo paid tribute to a "much-
OL,14,Floved son, brother, grandson, and
OL,15,Fnephew" and that he was "the sweetest,
OL,16,Fmost kindest boy ever".
